买了很多黄瓜，黄瓜最近很便宜吗？」 「不是呀，黄瓜还挺贵的」 「那为什么最近两天午饭晚饭都是黄瓜？」 「哦，我在家做习惯了，觉得省事儿」 「那这样吃下去我肯定能减肥了」 「哦，嫌弃最近都是黄瓜了，那明天换个菜」 原本对话到这里就差不多了，丈夫心疼他妈妈，非要进来拆台： 「你不是想减肥嘛，这样不是正好。妈，她本身就是想减肥的，没事儿」 后来我俩因为这件事情发生了争吵，他觉得我在逼迫他妈妈，觉得我有问题，嫌弃我说话不委婉，我觉得自己没问题，于是我决定到网上来提问一下，看看究竟是他有问题还是我有问题。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/659175009"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2cyioKvG+7IaEAMaCTEwODc2MTE3OSDix8CzBjAAOB9AC3IJNjU5MTc1MDA5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1718824555.852412", "card_id": "Q_654616896", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "清醒到极致的女主是怎样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654616896"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2cyioKvG+7IaEAMaCTEwNzc0ODI1OSCt1cOxBjAAOC9ADHIJNjU0NjE2ODk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1718824555.852577", "card_id": "Q_600831828", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 176}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么对人生的劝告?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "不管是学习恋爱婚姻工作为人处世 想知道有什么该注意的"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-62ffe059b1cf78765bd3fed1d8344098_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/600831828"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2cyioKvG+7IaEAMaCDk1Nzk4NjcwINHG/qIGMAA49gFADXIJNjAwODMxODI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1718824